{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/page,_N_T_/,_N_T_/index"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/__PAGE__","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/13v0w~23h0x1b.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/08.gnvx8bmp~~.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0i7-s3w3yb9nj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07lhk_q6pmm3r.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-0-mnb7a.6b7fe.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0wb8a~0m3ss9s.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Raja Mantri Chor Sipahi — Play online</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"A private, four-player online version of the classic Indian guessing game.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"heritage-app\"><header class=\"heritage-nav\"><a class=\"heritage-brand\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"brand-seal\">R</span><span><strong>RAJA MANTRI</strong><small>CHOR SIPAHI</small></span></a><div class=\"nav-center\"><span>4 PLAYER CLASSIC</span><i></i> <span>PRIVATE ROOMS</span><i></i> <span>NO ACCOUNTS</span></div><a class=\"rules-link\" href=\"#rules\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> How to play</a></header><main class=\"landing\"><section class=\"intro\"><p class=\"eyebrow\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg> A SCHOOLYARD CLASSIC, ONLINE</p><h1>Guess the thief.<br/><em>Guard your crown.</em></h1><p class=\"intro-copy\">Raja Mantri Chor Sipahi is the beloved four-player bluffing game. Deal secret roles, read your friends, and make one decisive guess.</p><div class=\"role-stamps\"><span>👑 Raja <b>1000</b></span><span>🗡️ Mantri <b>800</b></span><span>💰 Chor <b>?</b></span><span>🛡️ Sipahi <b>500</b></span></div></section><section class=\"paper-stack\"><div class=\"paper-note paper-back\"></div><div class=\"paper-note paper-main\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">ONE TABLE · FOUR FRIENDS</p><h3>Ready for a round?</h3><div class=\"paper-roles\"><span>👑</span><span>🗡️</span><span>💰</span><span>🛡️</span></div><p>Private role cards. No downloads. No account.</p></div></section></main><section class=\"lobby-area\"><div class=\"lobby-card\"><div class=\"lobby-card-heading\"><span class=\"card-number\">01</span><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">OPEN A TABLE</p><h2>Create a private room</h2></div></div><form class=\"lobby-form\"><label>Your name<input maxLength=\"24\" placeholder=\"e.g. Aanya\" required=\"\" value=\"\"/></label><label>How many rounds?<select><option value=\"3\">3 quick rounds</option><option value=\"5\" selected=\"\">5 classic rounds</option><option value=\"10\">10 long-game rounds</option></select></label><button class=\"heritage-button\" disabled=\"\">Create private room <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></form></div><div class=\"lobby-card join-card\"><div class=\"lobby-card-heading\"><span class=\"card-number\">02</span><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">HAVE A CODE?</p><h2>Join your friends</h2></div></div><form class=\"lobby-form\"><label>Room code<input inputMode=\"numeric\" placeholder=\"6 digits\" required=\"\" value=\"\"/></label><label>Your name<input maxLength=\"24\" placeholder=\"e.g. Kabir\" required=\"\" value=\"\"/></label><button class=\"outline-button\" disabled=\"\">Join room <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button></form></div><div class=\"open-rooms\"><div class=\"open-rooms-head\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">OPTIONAL</p><h2>Open tables</h2></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Refresh public rooms\">↻</button></div><div class=\"empty-rooms\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg><strong>No public table is waiting</strong><span>Create a private room and share its code instead.</span></div></div></section><section class=\"rules-section\" id=\"rules\"><p class=\"section-kicker\">THE CLASSIC RULES</p><h2>Four slips. One sharp guess.</h2><div class=\"rules-grid\"><article><span>01</span><i>👑</i><h3>Roles are dealt</h3><p>Exactly four players receive a secret Raja, Mantri, Chor or Sipahi card.</p></article><article><span>02</span><i>🗡️</i><h3>Mantri steps forward</h3><p>Raja calls for the Mantri. The Mantri reveals and prepares to identify Chor.</p></article><article><span>03</span><i>🕵️</i><h3>Make the guess</h3><p>The Mantri picks one of the two hidden players as Chor. Sipahi stays silent.</p></article><article><span>04</span><i>✦</i><h3>Count the points</h3><p>Raja gets 1000, Sipahi 500; Mantri gets 800 on a correct guess, otherwise Chor takes 800.</p></article></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/08.gnvx8bmp~~.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[66621,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0wb8a~0m3ss9s.js\\\"],\\\"RajaMantriApp\\\"]\\n5:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n6:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n8:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\"],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\na:I[97367,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\"],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\nc:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0dbhjjzl8qfwv.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/13v0w~23h0x1b.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\